The old Boston School System is a widely studied school system for the study of the Student Distribution Promblem.


What is understood about the agents in play.

Student:

Schools:

The very simplified game that simulates the Boston School System.

Everyone is given a score and a set of true School Preferences.
A set of "schools" with number of seats is given.
A scoring table for points given when you enter a school according to you true School preferences.
